race.comment: DEEL ME A QUEEN (2) has won 2/3 this preparation heavily bet and delivered with authority over 1750m last time. Suited by the step up to the middle distance, and the Bullock-Messara & Gavranich linkage is lethal. The one to beat. ZIZETTE (3) could prove the threat, dropping back several levels in grade. Needs this trip now and earlier this year, he just missed at Wyong over 2100m in a 64. FINAL IMPACT (1) raced forward winning over this distance at Wagga in a 58. Draws to advantage and can make the finish. DIPIERDOMENICO (5) just beat TYCOON LAD (9) over 1900m at Tamworth this grade. The latter raced favourite and draws an inside gate today. They can't be ruled out.
